title: (BONUS) Chatty Bros: Hot Thoughts on Bachelor Ep 4-7

description:
The Chatty Bros have broken into the studio again and they are ready to chat Matt James’ Bachelor Episodes 4-7! Grayson and Evan discuss a few of the high points of drama, who they believe to be frontrunner, how they feel about Matt, Heather’s entrance, who they were shocked to see go, and they go full #tangentialbro sharing stories of their past “swing and a miss” with love interests.
